They asked me to keep it confidential.

129
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,200
If there were any leak of information,

130
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:03,640
the criminal could have escaped.

131
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,280
Don't tell anyone else.

132
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:06,000
I got it.

133
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:10,120
Well,

134
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:11,720
I've an appointment

135
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,120
with the team.

136
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:13,720
We'll set off

137
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:14,640
early in the morning.

138
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,760
I must go shortly.

139
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:19,000
I haven't packed up my lugage yet.

140
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,640
