147
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:34,240
Why not just have a rest at home?

148
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,560
I don't need to haul bags this time,

149
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,720
They need someone who guards the goods

150
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:40,520
on the car in case of thieves

151
00:07:40,520 --> 00:07:41,560
when sleeping

152
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,800
at night.

153
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,160
I just need to guard the goods.

154
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,760
You should get sleep, too.

155
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:49,920
Not necessarily.

156
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,160
Yu,

157
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,960
if I stayed at home,

158
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:57,440
Erbai and others would come to see me

159
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,400
and buy things for me.

160
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,560
It's not easy for them to make money.

161
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:07,280
So I want to earn more money

162
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,280
and return

163
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,920
their favor.

164
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:11,600
What's more,

165
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,880
I can earn money this time

166
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:14,200
for delivering goods.

167
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,720
I heard them say

168
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:18,520
the top-scholar cakes of Fengjing are delicious.

169
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,480
I'll bring some cakes back

170
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,320
to you

171
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:21,400
and Erbai then.

172
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:22,920
Alright.

173
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,560
You're a good person.

174
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,720
But I'm worrying about you.

175
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:30,800
Make sure you eat well.

176
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:32,240
I got you.

177
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:34,720
Dongbao,

178
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,520
think over the baby's name

179
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:38,000
whenever you are free.

180
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,760
Once you name it,

181
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:40,640
I could talk to it

182
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:41,920
by its name.

183
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,520
OK.

184
00:08:45,040 --> 00:08:47,280
I'll think hard.

185
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:48,720
I will come up with 3 options for you

186
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,280
before I come back.

187
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,440
OK.

188
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:53,600
Let me listen to

189
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,840
my son.

190
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:56,280
It maybe a baby girl.

191
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:58,560
That's good, too.

192
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,000
I like both.

193
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,440
Don't worry about me.

194
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,280
Wait for me.

195
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,000
Minmin.

196
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,160
Dad.

197
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:33,160
Minmin,

198
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:37,920
it's the eight-treasure rice pudding in it.

199
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:39,760
Your friend is pregnant,

200
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:41,080
so, I bring some more for her.

201
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:42,800
Thank you, dad.

202
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,480
Hurry back.

203
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:45,720
Wait,

204
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:48,680
what would you like to eat as dinner?

205
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:51,760
I want to have some soup.

206
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,320
I want warm soup made by yellow croaker.

207
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:54,800
I got it.

208
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:55,960
I'll cook it for you.

209
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,640
I'll go back home soon.

210
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:58,520
OK.

211
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:11,960
Did Dongbao tell you

212
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,000
when he would go back home?

213
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:14,880
He said it just needs 2 or 3 days.

214
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,960
Maybe he will come back tomorrow.

215
00:10:17,280 --> 00:10:18,720
Dongbao said that

216
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:20,000
he'd bring tasty food back from Jinshanwei.

217
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:22,120
Minmin,

218
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,760
the rice pudding is so delicious.

219
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:24,800
It's sweet.

220
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:26,760
It's my dad's cook.

221
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:29,520
You have a good appetite.

222
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,440
I don't know why.

223
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:34,000
Others vomit a alot when they are pregnant.

224
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,080
But I'm different.

225
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:36,320
I'm full of vigor.

226
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,160
That's very good sign.

227
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:40,000
You have a good appetite and the baby feels happy.

228
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:43,240
Have you given a name?

229
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,280
Not yet.

230
00:10:44,760 --> 00:10:45,320
Dongbao said that

231
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,840
he would think about it on his way.

232
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:48,520
And he made sure that he could offer me 3 names.

233
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,360
You must be very happy.

234
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:13,760
Get out of the car.

235
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:20,360
Go back home.

236
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,920
It's cold outside.

237
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:22,760
It doesn't matter.

238
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:23,760
I'll go with you till the end of the alley.

239
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:25,200
I should have some exercise.

240
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,520
OK, you should.

241
00:11:26,760 --> 00:11:27,520
Brother Lu,

242
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:29,200
