243
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:30,040
Where's Dongbao?

244
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:32,160
We didn't go to Jinshanwei.

245
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:33,920
Didn't Dongbao tell you?

246
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:36,080
He didn't go back home at all.

247
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:37,280
Really?

248
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:38,520
Then where did he go?

249
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,080
Didn't he go with you

250
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,440
to haul goods in Jinshanwei?

251
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,400
Don't mention it.

252
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:44,440
When we gathered that night,

253
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:46,800
the boss said the business was canceled.

254
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,040
So, we went back home

255
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:49,560
after that.

256
00:11:50,040 --> 00:11:50,840
Maybe

257
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:51,320
Dongbao had another work

258
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:52,240
to do.

259
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:53,160
No.

260
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:53,960
Lu.

