264
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:56,480
Yu,

265
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,520
Keep asking the others.

266
00:11:57,520 --> 00:11:58,400
I gotta go.

267
00:11:59,200 --> 00:11:59,720
No.

268
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:01,840
He neither hauled goods nor went home.

269
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,280
Where could he be?

270
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:04,920
Yu, don't worry.

271
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:06,600
Will it possible for Dongbao

272
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:07,600
to go to another team?

273
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:10,200
Minmin, his hand was injured

274
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,480
and I'm pregnant now.

275
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,640
He wouldn't go anywhere

276
00:12:12,640 --> 00:12:13,760
without telling me.

277
00:12:13,760 --> 00:12:14,680
And he left

278
00:12:14,680 --> 00:12:15,560
in the middle of night.

279
00:12:15,560 --> 00:12:16,760
