281
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,800
or met someone

282
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:21,000
before he left home?

283
00:12:25,160 --> 00:12:26,040
Let's talk in the room.

284
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:28,800
Take care.

285
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,000
Minmin,

286
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:34,680
Dongbao had found some smuggling goods

287
00:12:34,680 --> 00:12:36,440
in the warehouse that night.

288
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:38,160
He said it related to the military supplies.

289
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:40,160
And he reported to the Shanghai Customs District immediately.

290
00:12:40,560 --> 00:12:41,120
Well,

291
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:42,120
did it bring some trouble

292
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:42,840
to him?

293
00:12:44,160 --> 00:12:45,400
What's that?

294
00:12:45,400 --> 00:12:46,560
It was a case,

295
00:12:46,560 --> 00:12:48,320
in which Dongbao said there were bristles,

