00:33:47,360 --> 00:33:48,520
always the Hua family.

591
00:33:53,600 --> 00:33:54,280
So all our families

592
00:33:54,280 --> 00:33:55,440
know this?

593
00:33:58,480 --> 00:33:59,600
Mom doesn't know.

594
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:03,040
Dad was also a soldier.

595
00:34:03,800 --> 00:34:05,680
He fought in the Northern Expedition with the former premier,

596
00:34:06,360 --> 00:34:07,760
and he knew how difficult it was

597
00:34:07,760 --> 00:34:09,040
for China to achieve unification.

598
00:34:09,040 --> 00:34:10,600
Did those hardships end up

599
00:34:10,600 --> 00:34:12,600
being for the sake of today's business?

600
00:34:12,600 --> 00:34:13,840
The great adventure

601
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:15,040
had been accomplished,

602
00:34:15,040 --> 00:34:16,320
and everyone wants to

603
00:34:16,320 --> 00:34:17,240
take some profits from it.

604
00:34:17,240 --> 00:34:17,960
What's wrong with that?

605
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:19,040
Why can't we?

606
00:34:20,080 --> 00:34:21,440
You don't understand this,

607
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:22,680
but it doesn't mean it's wrong.

608
00:34:22,680 --> 00:34:23,320
It's just

609
00:34:23,320 --> 00:34:24,800
you can't understand.

610
00:34:27,600 --> 00:34:29,600
Don't think what you see

611
00:34:29,600 --> 00:34:31,440
and what you hear is the truth,

612
00:34:32,440 --> 00:34:34,360
and don't use it to judge me.

613
00:34:35,360 --> 00:34:36,800
What is the truth?

614
00:34:38,040 --> 00:34:39,480
Is there a second option

615
00:34:39,480 --> 00:34:41,040
when we face the possible fall of the nation?

616
00:34:42,160 --> 00:34:43,240
And if we even need to

617
00:34:43,240 --> 00:34:44,200
talk about positions on this matter,

618
00:34:44,200 --> 00:34:45,600
talk about right and wrong,

619
00:34:46,960 --> 00:34:48,600
we are fundamentally different.

620
00:34:48,600 --> 00:34:49,840
I'm your brother.

621
00:34:52,160 --> 00:34:53,600
We just have different ideas.

622
00:34:54,120 --> 00:34:54,840
Don't regard me

623
00:34:54,840 --> 00:34:56,080
as your enemy so easily.

624
00:34:56,080 --> 00:34:58,240
This is not a concept, but a bottom line.

625
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:01,080
"Internal disunity dissolves at the threat of external invasion."

626
00:35:02,080 --> 00:35:03,320
Communists have been pressed

627
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:04,600
by you to the end,

628
00:35:04,600 --> 00:35:05,960
but still spare no efforts

629
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:07,040
to resist against Japanese.

630
00:35:08,160 --> 00:35:09,360
While the pillars of our party and state

631
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:10,680
smuggle military supplies

632
00:35:10,680 --> 00:35:11,800
to the Japanese.

633
00:35:12,080 --> 00:35:13,800
"Cooperate in good faith, and collective prosperity."

634
00:35:14,480 --> 00:35:16,040
How am I suppsed to understand you?

635
00:35:16,720 --> 00:35:17,320
Do you want to be a traitor

636
00:35:17,320 --> 00:35:19,240
and a flunky of the Japanese?

637
00:35:20,200 --> 00:35:21,200
What are you saying?

638
00:35:41,720 --> 00:35:42,880
Don't think I won't beat you

639
00:35:42,880 --> 00:35:43,840
as you learned something

640
00:35:43,840 --> 00:35:45,200
in military school.

641
00:36:08,840 --> 00:36:10,600
You go back to school by my car now.

642
00:36:11,680 --> 00:36:13,840
Mom told me before my departure,

643
00:36:14,240 --> 00:36:15,480
that no matter what happens,

644
00:36:15,480 --> 00:36:16,960
I have to protect you.

645
00:36:17,280 --> 00:36:18,760
You can go back to school

646
00:36:18,760 --> 00:36:19,800
unscathed now,

647
00:36:20,200 --> 00:36:21,240
because I still remember

648
00:36:21,240 --> 00:36:22,600
you are my brother.

649
00:36:24,920 --> 00:36:26,200
Since I was little,

650
00:36:29,560 --> 00:36:30,720
I've always been knowing

651
00:36:30,720 --> 00:36:32,040
what I was missing.

652
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:37,920
I don't have companionship from parents,

653
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:40,920
and I don't have a family

654
00:36:40,920 --> 00:36:42,320
have dinner at table, and talk.

655
00:36:46,600 --> 00:36:48,040
But I have an elder brother.

656
00:36:51,720 --> 00:36:53,680
When I got stuck in the car,

657
00:36:55,040 --> 00:36:56,280
he would pull the door down

658
00:36:56,280 --> 00:36:58,080
to get me out.

659
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:01,600
And when no one

660
00:37:01,600 --> 00:37:03,200
would let me join the navy,

661
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:07,400
he would strive for my dream

662
00:37:07,400 --> 00:37:08,720
against everyone.

663
00:37:13,920 --> 00:37:15,720
When I reported to School of Mining Command,

664
00:37:18,240 --> 00:37:19,840
he drove me to school

665
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:21,200
for straight two days and nights,

666
00:37:23,680 --> 00:37:25,600
and took photos with me at the school gate.

667
00:37:32,200 --> 00:37:33,680
You are the only person

668
00:37:33,680 --> 00:37:35,680
I trust and depend on in this family.

669
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:41,120
Bro,

670
00:37:44,200 --> 00:37:45,600
why you?

671
00:37:53,480 --> 00:37:54,240
I don't live

672
00:37:54,240 --> 00:37:55,480
in a utopia,

673
00:37:58,040 --> 00:37:58,840
and I know someone

674
00:37:58,840 --> 00:38:00,480
might have been doing this,

675
00:38:04,800 --> 00:38:05,960
but why you?

676
00:38:41,840 --> 00:38:43,040
You and me

677
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:47,480
are totally different.

678
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:52,080
I know we are different,

679
00:38:54,880 --> 00:38:55,440
and I never think of

680
00:38:55,440 --> 00:38:56,800
being a person like you.

681
00:39:00,920 --> 00:39:02,120
But this never affects

682
00:39:02,120 --> 00:39:03,600
your image in my heart.

683
00:39:07,040 --> 00:39:08,600
I can take a bullet for you,

684
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:13,320
but what you saw today

685
00:39:16,480 --> 00:39:17,600
won't change.

686
00:39:20,040 --> 00:39:21,320
It won't change today,

687
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:24,040
and neither in the future.

688
00:39:41,040 --> 00:39:41,840
Hua Zhen,

689
00:39:43,000 --> 00:39:44,920
you are in danger now.

690
00:39:47,200 --> 00:39:48,080
Go back to school.

691
00:39:53,440 --> 00:39:54,200
Just go.

692
00:39:57,440 --> 00:39:58,200
Go.

693
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:20,600
I didn't want to tell you

694
00:40:22,200 --> 00:40:23,960
that Luo Minmin was arrested.

695
00:40:27,080 --> 00:40:27,840
What?

696
00:40:28,200 --> 00:40:29,800
If you go back to school now,

697
00:40:30,240 --> 00:40:31,480
I will call them

698
00:40:31,480 --> 00:40:32,600
and ask them

699
00:40:32,840 --> 00:40:33,920
to keep her alive.

700
00:40:34,200 --> 00:40:36,080
If you continue to waste time here,

701
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:38,080
she probably won't survive tonight.

702
00:40:38,080 --> 00:40:39,080
What's wrong with Luo Minmin?

703
00:40:40,160 --> 00:40:41,800
You take my car back to school now.

704
00:40:42,680 --> 00:40:44,200
I have something to do here.

705
00:40:44,920 --> 00:40:46,200
As long as my men tell me

706
00:40:46,200 --> 00:40:48,200
that they see you entering the school,

707
00:40:48,440 --> 00:40:49,760
I'll immediately call them

708
00:40:49,760 --> 00:40:50,560
to let her go.

709
00:40:52,600 --> 00:40:53,840
What happened to Luo Minmin?

710
00:40:54,200 --> 00:40:55,040
Where is she?

711
00:40:59,760 --> 00:41:00,520
Answer me!

712
00:41:01,120 --> 00:41:02,800
You stay a minute longer,

713
00:41:03,160 --> 00:41:04,720
and she'll die a minute sooner.

714
00:41:05,640 --> 00:41:07,320
Is it Tan Shiyuan or Nakamura Naoki?

715
00:41:08,200 --> 00:41:09,240
Or you?

716
00:41:10,640 --> 00:41:12,120
What happened to Luo Minmin?

717
00:41:12,120 --> 00:41:14,080
You're wasting her time.

718
00:41:29,000 --> 00:41:29,840
Made up your mind?

719
00:41:32,280 --> 00:41:33,320
Is she alive?

720
00:41:34,080 --> 00:41:35,080
Alive for now.

721
00:41:36,520 --> 00:41:37,160
You promise me.

722
00:41:37,640 --> 00:41:38,440
I promise,

723
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:41,080
as long as you go back to school,

724
00:41:41,840 --> 00:41:43,400
I'll ask them to let her go.

725
00:41:54,600 --> 00:41:55,800
Send him back to school

726
00:41:55,800 --> 00:41:56,680
and tell Master Hu

727
00:41:56,680 --> 00:41:57,840
not to allow him to step out of the school

728
00:41:57,840 --> 00:41:59,520
without my order.

729
00:41:59,920 --> 00:42:00,520
Yes,sir.

730
00:42:06,040 --> 00:42:06,840
And,

731
00:42:08,840 --> 00:42:10,600
never repeat

732
00:42:11,000 --> 00:42:12,040
what you said.

